## 🇺🇸 **ENGLISH VERSION**

**Privacy Policy**

**1. General Information**
This privacy policy provides information about how personal data of users using the Televizle mobile application ("App") is collected, used, and protected. By using the App, you agree to this privacy policy.

**2. Information We Collect**

**2.1 Automatically Collected Information:**
• Device information (model, operating system version)
• App usage statistics
• Location information (country-based, optional)
• IP address
• App performance data

**2.2 User-Provided Information:**
• Language preferences
• Favorite channel lists
• App settings

**3. Purpose of Information Use**
• Provide core app functionality
• Personalize user experience
• Offer relevant content recommendations
• Provide technical support
• Improve app performance
• Fulfill legal obligations

**4. Data Sharing**
Your personal data is not shared with third parties. Limited data sharing may occur only in the following situations:
• Due to legal requirements
• With service providers that provide the app's technical infrastructure
• With advertising networks for ad display (anonymous data)

**5. Data Security**
The security of your personal data is our priority. Industry-standard security measures are taken to protect your data:
• SSL/TLS encryption
• Secure data storage
• Access control
• Regular security updates

**6. Cookies and Tracking Technologies**
The App may use cookies and similar technologies to improve user experience. These technologies:
• Store session information
• Remember user preferences
• Analyze app performance

**7. User Rights**
You have the following rights regarding your personal data:
• Right to access your data
• Right to rectify data
• Right to delete data
• Right to object to data processing
• Right to data portability

**8. Policy Changes**
This privacy policy may be updated from time to time. Significant changes will be notified within the app. The updated policy takes effect on the date it is published.

**9. Contact**
For privacy-related questions: umut4app@gmail.com
If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us.


